VCS
Journey through
the Decade
Hnh trnh 10 nm - 1 thp k ca nhng phn u bn b, 1 thp k ca n lc khng nh tn tui, tr tu ngi Vn trong nc v quc t. 1 thp k vi khi u t mt ban ATTT 6 ngi ti Cng ty ANM hn 500 ngi vi nhng thnh tch vang danh:
2014.Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel c thnh lp vi s mnh bo v an ton thng tin trng yu cho tp on
Ngy 14/08/2014, T Vin thng Qun i k Q s 1762/Q-VTQ_TCNL thnh lp TT. An ninh mng Viettel. Vi nhim v: Xy dng cng c gii php phng th cho T trc cc nguy c tn cng trn khng gian mng; thc hin nh gi c lp, kim nh cc h thng nhm pht hin nguy c, bo v ATTT cho T; nghin cu xy dng pht trin, ng gi gii php sn phm dch v ATTT a vo trin khai trn mng li; sn sng lc lng m bo an ninh trn khng gian mng.
2015. Thnh lp Trung tm Gm st v Phn ng trn khng gian mng (Security Intelligence & Response Center) - Tri tim ca Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel
Lm th no kim sot tp trung vn ATTT trong cc h thng ca tp on vi iu kin c th nh ca Viettel: nhiu mi trng, quy trnh v nn tng khc nhau, tri rng nhiu quc gia, v cng phc tp, m li khng th mua ngoi v khng p ng c yu cu quan trng ""lm ch cng ngh"" cng nh ""bo mt ti a"" cho h thng c th Viettel?"" Anh Trnh Hoi Nam, Nguyn Vn Huy, inh Hu Cng cng cc ng nghip ti Trung tm An ninh mng nhn nhim v vi t tng n nhn thch thc ln. T ""s tn nhim v tinh thn bn b - khng c vic g kh, ch s lng khng bn"", trung tm gim st tp trung c hnh thnh - l tp hp con ngi v gii php ATTT i km vi b quy trnh h tr x l tng t chun GNOC (Global Network Operation Center, cho php o lng mc an ton v gim st c vn ATTT ca cc h thng nhm nh gi chnh xc vn ATTT trn ton b mng li (cho hn 3.000 my ch ca Viettel ti 10 quc gia) - iu m cha n v no ti Vit Nam trin khai c ti thi im .
2016. X l thnh cng s c Vietnam Airlines. Thnh vin ca TT ANM tm ra 8 l hng zero-day ca cc h thng ln nh Facebook, Zimbra, Adobe Reader, PHP

- Ngy 29/7/2016, Vietnam Airlines gp s c tn cng mng tm c quc gia. i ng An ninh mng Viettel - lc ny tr thnh Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel - dnh khong 1 thng h tr Vietnam Airlines khc phc s c v ngn chn nguy c b tn cng tr li. Mt thng chin u bn b, vi 30 ngi/ngy. Trong 2 tun u, anh em gn nh khng ng, cng lm vic hn 20h/ngy. Lin tc thay nhau chp mt ti ch lm vic trong phng my ch vi nhit trung bnh 10-15 , gia ma h! ""Ln x, quyt lit, bn b, k vai st cnh, hi sinh nim vui c nhn v li ch chung"" chnh l keyword Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel x l thnh cng s c VNA. S kin chnh l s Khng nh cho nng lc + tinh thn ""striving"" ca ngi VCS. Khng nh s trng thnh vt bc c v k nng x l s c v kh nng pht trin sn phm, gii php ATTT - ca ngi Vit - cho ngi Vit.

- Vi s n lc bn b, lm vic kh vi tinh thn ""D qua sng"", nhng l hng 0-day bt u xut hin nh: l hng nghim trng trn Apache Struts ca Phm Vn Khnh (2015), li 0-day trn nn tng PHP ca anh Nguyn Hng Quang (2016), li Virtualbox trn nn tng Oracle ca Ng Anh Huy (2017),... nh tip la am m v t tin, xy chc nn mng nhm pht trin i ng nhn s ""lm bo mt"" world-class, tp trung nghin cu chuyn su v tm kim l hng quan trng rt thnh cng nh ny hm nay.

2017. Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel k kt hp ng kinh doanh bn ngoi u tin
Trong qu trnh x l s c ca Vietnam Airlines, rt nhiu gii php t ch - pht trin cho ni b Viettel c mang ra p dng trc tip trong qu trnh x l s c v t nhng thnh cng ln. Nhn thy sn phm, dch v ni b gii quyt vn cho nhiu t chc, n v khc nhau , Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel bt u trin khai cung cp dch v, sn phm ra bn ngoi. K kt hp ng kinh doanh u tin vi khch hnh chnh l Vietnam Airlines. t tin cho vic thnh lp cng ty v m rng m hnh kinh doanh vo nm 2018.
2017. Bo m ATTT cho s kin ""Tun l Cp cao Din n hp tc kinh t chu -Thi Bnh Dng (APEC) 2017""
Vi s mnh phng s quc gia, m bo An ton thng tin trn khng gian mng, VCS ng vai tr then cht trong vic m bo An ton thng tin H tng Vin thng v Cng ngh thng tin xuyn sut tun l hi ngh cp cao Apec - Hi ngh . Mt thng trc s kin, Team VCS tp trung xy dng kch bn ng cu trong trng hp b tn cng, din tp gi lp tn cng vo h thng ti trung tm bo ch, t xem xt cc kh nng, tnh hung b tn cng, ph hoi trn thc t cng nh trn khng gian mng xy dng cc phng n ng ph khi tnh hung xy ra. Khng ch ln k hoch bo v, nng cao gim st, m bo tt nht, an ton nht cho cc trang thit b, VCS cn tp trung tng cng bo v an ton thng tin, an ninh mng trong cc trng hp b hacker tn cng nhm gy gin on thng tin hay chim quyn kim sot h thng.
2018. Cng ty c thnh lp. Nhn C thi ua ca B Quc Phng
Vo ngy 14/08/2018. Trung tm An ninh mng Viettel chnh thc chuyn mnh, tr thnh Cng ty An ninh mng Viettel (Viettel Cyber Security). Vi gn 200 nhn s, trong c nhng chuyn gia ngi Vit hng u trong lnh vc an ninh mng, s hu nhiu chng ch an ton thng tin uy tn v danh ting c ton th gii cng nhn nh CISSP, CCIE, CEH, Security+ i ng chuyn gia ca cng ty cng khai thc hn 100 l hng 0-day - l nhng li cha tng c pht hin trn th gii ca cc h thng bo mt uy tn ton cu. Nhiu l hng tm ra c Google, Facebook, Microsoft vinh danh v trao thng. Mi nm, h thng phng th ca Cng ty An ninh mng Viettel ngn chn c hn 25.000 cuc tn cng an ninh mng ca hacker (tin tc) trn th gii vo h thng ca Viettel v khch hng. Bn cnh , VCS tp trung t ch xy dng v pht trin gii php dch v: H thng gim st An ton thng tin tp trung (SOC); H thng gim st v bo v cho mng vin thng, chng lu cc; H thng gim st v bo v ng dng Web trn nn tng in ton m my; H thng qun l An ton thng tin cho mng Vn phng cng vi nhm dch v chnh bao gm: Dch v gim st v x l s c an ton thng tin 24/7; Dch v kim nh nh gi an ton thng tin cho h thng v ng dng; Dch v r sot g b m c Nhiu sn phm t cc gii thng danh gi trn th gii nh Gii ng IT World Awards 2016, gii Bc Stevie Awards 2017; v cc gii thng dnh cho cc hacker m trng trn th gii nh White Hat 9, Snatching The Hat.
2019. H tr x l s c ca Bank X, to tin "tin tng v ng hnh" vi vi nhm khch hng kh tnh.
Cng ty mi bt u kinh doanh bn ngoi, nhiu sn phm v dch v cha hon thin. Tuy nhin, khng nh v th tin phong v s 1 Vit Nam, VCS cn chinh phc tri tim khch hng kh. 2019, Bank X gp s c. VCS tham gia h tr x l s c vi tinh thn h tr ht mnh, d cho l i tc hay cha. Trong thi gian x l s c, Anh em lun tc trc 24/7, thm ch nhn s ca VCS lm vic ti Bank X cn nhiu hn chnh nhn s ca h. Vi s nhit tnh, tn ty v kh nng x l s c rt tt, VCS thuyt phc c c cn b k thut ln qun l cp cao ca Bank X khin h chuyn sang s dng dch v ca VCS. Qu trnh ng hnh x l s c trit gip VCS chng minh c nng lc, xy dng nim tin vng chc, tha mn c khch hng kh tnh nht. Vng bc trn con ng khng nh v th s 1 Vit Nam.
2020. Trin khai Msuite - Cung cp gii php lm vic t xa trong trng thi dch bnh, gp vai tr quan trng trong trng thi bnh thng mi
Trong bi cnh i dch Covid-19, hu ht cc doanh nghip, t chc u tin hnh dch chuyn sang hnh thc lm vic t xa. T , vic kt ni cc thit b t h thng mng bn ngoi n mng ni b tim n nhiu im yu v bo mt cng nh cc nguy c l lt, mt an ton thng tin. Vi s mnh bo v An ton thng tin ca ngi Vit trn khng gian, VCS pht trin v cho ra mt gii php Viettel Enterprise Mobility Suite (VCS M-Suite), gp phn bo mt mng li ATTT trong qu trnh kt ni v truy cp t xa ca DN, gii quyt c bi ton bnh thng mi trong iu kin dch bnh din bin phc tp.
2021. VCS k kt Hp ng quc t u tin.
Thng 12/2021, VCS chnh thc k c hp ng quc t u tin vi i tc ti th trng Nam Phi. y c coi l mt bc chuyn mnh quan trng ca VCS t mt nh cung cp sn phm dch v ni a chnh thc thm nhp th trng quc t. Du mc cho kht vng a VCS tr thnh cng ty ton cu.
2023. V ch P2W, ln nh realworld sau 3 nm th sc trn sn chi hng u th gii.
VCS - Team Viettel v ch P2O 2023 t i hnh 14 thnh vin vi tui i cn rt tr 75% th h Gen Z, thnh vin ln tui nht l 34, thnh vin nh tui nht mi ch 20. v ch sn chi bo mt uy tn hng u th gii, ngi VCS phi tm ra nhng l hng c o nht khng mt ai trn th gii tm ra c. ""Chc chn lnh vc an ninh mng cn rt rng ln, cn nhiu thch thc. Nhng thch thc cng ln, cng thi thc khao kht chinh phc. Chuyn gia ti VCS s tham gia su, rng hn na, khng ch dng li IOT m cn l cng nghip, nng lng, in tip tc khng nh nng lc v v th v an ton thng tin cho Viettel v cho ton Vit Nam trn trng quc t.
2024 v tng lai: Vng bc, kin nh Conquer the world!
Hng ti nm 2025 v 2030, bn cnh nhng nhng mc tiu nh lng c nh Top 1 th trng Vit, Top 3 ng Nam , kht vng ca ngi VCS chnh l chuyn mnh sang m hnh cng ty kinh doanh ton cu ng ngha. Kinh doanh ton cu l phi c mt tp khch hng ton cu, phi c h thng quy trnh ton cu, nhn s ton cu, khng ch ngi Vit Nam m c ngi nc ngoi, cc bn c th di chuyn ti cc vn phng ton cu mt cch rt linh hot. a VCS c li th cnh tranh VN l mt mi trng lm vic a quc gia."

H Thu - Pht trin vn ha
"Ti lm vic vi VCS" - cng vic m ti lm mi ngy l t nhng cu hi cho cng vic ca mnh, l mt t giy trng lun ""lm mi"" n mi ngy. Cng vic cng kh th c bt u kin nhn, t m vi n th s dn dn s c bc tin v dn d s c gi tr. Lm vic vi con ngi VCS, SPDV ca VCS, Mi trng VCS v Gi tr ca VCS mun mu cho cng vic thit k ca chnh ti. VCS lun l iu ti lun t ho c lm vic cng v kin tc cng.
Thy Nguyn - Senior Tester
VCS thc y ch lm vic chuyn nghip, ci thin chuyn mn v kim th hiu nng v k nng qun l cht lng ton trnh. Lin tc cho ch mi trng tm ti ra cc phng php/cng c thc thi mi, hiu qu. Chng ti, ch s "ng hnh" cng cc bn tr ti VCS Test comm, v ch chung "cng test cng t bug".
Nguyn Anh T - Threat Hunting
5 nm cng VCS, th li nht l mi quan h vi ng nghip siu nhn nh anh Quangnh, Thanhdo, Longhuy Mi ngi thng tnh gp vo li sai. Gip em pht trin nng lc rt tt. M rng kh nng t duy. Tip thu kinh nghim c c kt t chuyn gia. Hin ti,e cn tp trung nghin cu v giao lu vi chuyn gia quc t nng cao nng lc bn thn khng nh nng lc ca TI, ngang vai vi ln quc t.
Quang Huy - EDR - endpoint detection & Respond
Ngi c sc nh hng ti em - anh T - anh l sp, l mentor, l mt ng anh. A cho em mt nh hng pht trin ngh nghip ph hp vi mindset ca mnh. Bit mnh c im mnh g v cn pht trin g? Em sec ci thin s n nh ca h thng, tng ph v detection, gim l lt tn cng. ti u ngun alert gim ti vn hnh, ch ng hc hi, nng cao nng lc chuyn mn.
Thu Phng - K hoch quy trnh
